					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p219289">Re: Suckerpinch's Reverse Emulation Videos</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=219289&amp;sid=5bfb884166dfd575eb72413b953b263b#p219289"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Fri Jun 01, 2018 5:34 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
